1
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:27,480
This bloodstain looks like it's been here for years

2
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:40,920
Fifth Concubine

3
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,680
Fifth Concubine, you shouldn't be here

4
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:48,080
The tea room is over there

5
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,760
This Western-style house is too big

6
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,280
I just got here, so I keep getting lost

7
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:53,000
Please don't go wandering around again

8
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,960
The Wang Family's clan discipline is very strict

9
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,280
Even a concubine like you

10
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,560
If you break the rules, you'll be punished too

11
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:03,280
Has any concubine broken the rules before?

12
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,240
Butler Du gave orders before

13
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:10,320
In the Wang Family, you must never mention former concubines

14
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,480
It is taboo

15
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,800
Then I'll be blunt

16
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:27,000
Ever since that bone-gathering ritual back then

17
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,520
Our Eldest Young Master has gone mad

18
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,880
Strange things have kept happening in the house

19
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,560
Our master has been deeply uneasy

20
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:38,880
A clear conscience fears no ghost at the door

21
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,520
Master Wang is feeling uneasy

22
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,760
I'm afraid there is another reason

23
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,360
Our master is kindhearted

24
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:50,840
He always feels he wronged the Eldest Young Master and Miss Shuang'er

25
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:53,160
So he wants to ask you to perform the bone-gathering ritual for them

26
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,200
Our Wang Family is showing such sincerity

27
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,280
Surely you won't refuse

28
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,960
The Wang Family's sincerity

29
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:05,040
Is just like it was three years ago

30
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,840
Mr. Zheng, please come in

31
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,320
Please rest here for a while

32
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,880
Our master has some matters to deal with

33
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,760
He'll be here shortly, please wait

34
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,240
Xu Nan, what's wrong?

35
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,560
I shouldn't have treated you that way before

36
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,320
Will you take me away from here?

37
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,680
What are you doing?

38
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,200
Fifth Concubine, what are you doing?

39
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,200
Didn't you want to take me away?

40
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,480
You are already a married woman

41
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,760
Please have some self-respect

42
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,240
Master

43
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,680
Are you satisfied now, Master?

44
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:16,120
You are smarter than your sister

45
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,120
I'm telling you

46
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:21,680
As long as you obediently remain my Fifth Concubine

47
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,720
I won't keep holding on to the past

48
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,640
I'm warning you

49
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,760
Don't you dare fool around under my nose

50
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,960
I, Wang Shengchang

51
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,480
When dealing with such people

52
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,880
Have plenty of ways

53
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:48,040
Rest assured, Master, I won't

54
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:04,200
Three years ago, the bone-gathering ritual failed

55
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:07,640
My Sanming met an untimely death

56
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,920
To dispel that woman's resentment

57
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:15,080
we buried that woman with my Sanming

58
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,520
Who knew that woman

59
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,240
would not rest in peace

60
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,760
and keeps harming people

61
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,200
When my master was still alive

62
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,160
he taught me a secret art

63
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,560
that may dispel Miss Shuang'er's resentment

64
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:32,680
As long as it keeps the Wang Family safe

65
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:35,200
money is no issue

66
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,600
Forgive me, Master Wang, but one question

67
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,720
Miss Shuang'er

68
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:45,280
what grievance keeps haunting the Wang Family?

69
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:49,160
What do you mean by that?

70
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,440
Please do not be angry, Master Wang

71
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,160
To dispel resentment

72
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:56,400
I must know the dead one's grievance

73
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:00,640
Her death was only an accident

74
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,160
There was no grievance at all

75
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:07,960
Miss Shuang'er was your Wang Family's daughter-in-law

76
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,560
If it was only an accident

77
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,520
her resentment could not be this deep

78
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,760
lingering without fading

79
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:14,280
and still killing people

80
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:15,880
Impudent

81
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:19,720
That woman was merely unwilling to accept it

82
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,720
Just do your bone-gathering ritual properly

83
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,600
What you should not ask

84
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,840
do not ask

85
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:27,760
Three years ago, if your master had not failed

86
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,080
the Wang Family would not have had these troubles

87
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,280
The master summoned you here

88
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,280
to clean up the aftermath

89
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:36,360
not to pry into everything

90
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,840
Please do not blame me, Master Wang

91
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,320
I spoke out of turn

92
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:42,320
When do you plan to do the bone-gathering ritual?

93
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,680
This matter cannot be rushed

94
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:47,400
The resentment in this residence is too heavy

95
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,680
I need to stay with the Wang Family for a few days

96
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,040
and perform some rites each day

97
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,640
to dispel the resentment

98
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,240
only then can I do the bone-gathering ritual

99
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,480
This brat has gotten smarter in three years

100
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,840
Everyone in the neighborhood says

101
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:06,920
his master, Master Cao, lost his life because he did

102
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,160
the Wang Family's bone-gathering ritual three years ago

103
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,680
Because the boy was scared

104
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,240
he did not dare return to Nanwan Town for three years

105
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,600
and now he suddenly comes back

106
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,800
he must be plotting something

107
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:18,040
Tell him he had better behave himself

108
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:23,200
or I will send him to join his master in the underworld

109
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,280
All right
